Package chord.analyses.invk

Facts of method invocation quads.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DomI Domain of method invocation quads.
RelInstI Relation containing all method invocation quads whose target is an instance method.
RelMI Relation containing each tuple (m,i) such that method m contains method invocation quad i.
RelPI Relation containing each tuple (p,i) such that the quad at program point p is method invocation quad i.
RelSpecIM Relation containing each tuple (i,m) such that m is the resolved method of method invocation quad i of kind INVK_SPECIAL.
RelStatIM Relation containing each tuple (i,m) such that m is the resolved method of method invocation quad i of kind INVK_STATIC.
RelVirtIM Relation containing each tuple (i,m) such that m is the resolved method of method invocation quad i of kind INVK_VIRTUAL or INVK_INTERFACE.
StubRewrite Used to rewrite method calls, to facilitate stub implementations or analyzable models.
